.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-9::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  dressmaker, entrepreneur, librarian, videographer
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: aconite, dahlia, marigold, bellflower
1. the librarian is between the person who growsaconite and the dressmaker##2
2. the person who growsbellflower is on the left of the dressmaker##1
3. the videographer is on the right of the dressmaker##1
4. the person who growsaconite is on the left of the person who growsbellflower##1
5. the dressmaker is on the left of the person who growsmarigold##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |     2     |     3      |      4       |
| Job         | entrepreneur | librarian | dressmaker | videographer |
| Flower   | aconite         | bellflower       | dahlia    | marigold         |

