.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-10::.
There 4 different types of food: avocado, garlic, peach, plum
The people have 4 different jobs:  paramedic, accountant, scientist, manager
1. the accountant is on the right of the person eating plum##1
2. the scientist is on the right of the person eating peach##1
3. the person eating avocado is on the right of the person eating garlic##1
4. the scientist is on the right of the accountant##1
5. the accountant is between the person eating garlic and the manager##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |     2      |    3     |    4     |
| Food    | plum   | peach      | garlic   | avocado  |
| Job   | manager | accountant | scientist | paramedic |

