.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-11::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: hiking, reading, magic-tricks, video-games
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: animation, fantasy, superhero, time-travel
1. the person watching time-travel movies is on the right of the person watching fantasy movies##1
2. the person who's hobby is reading is between the person who's hobby is video-games and the person who's hobby is hiking##2
3. the person watching fantasy movies is on the right of the person watching superhero movies##1
4. the person watching superhero movies is on the right of the person who's hobby is hiking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |    3    |      4      |
| Hobby          | hiking     | reading | video-games   | magic-tricks        |
| Movie-Genre   | animation | superhero   | fantasy | time-travel |

