.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-12::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: marigold, amaryllis, poppy, dahlia
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: gospel, pop, punk, trance
1. the fan of punk is the person who growsamaryllis##1
2. the fan of pop is on the left of the fan of trance##1
3. the fan of gospel is the person who growsmarigold##1
4. the person who growspoppy is the fan of pop##1
5. the fan of gospel is on the right of the person who growsdahlia##1
6. the fan of pop is between the person who growsamaryllis and the person who growsdahlia##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2    |    3    |     4      |
| Flower         | amaryllis | poppy | dahlia | marigold |
| Music-Genre   | punk          | pop     | trance  | gospel     |

