1. the person drinking iced-tea is the person watching martial-arts movies##1
2. the person watching animation movies is between the person watching spy movies and the person watching epic movies##2
3. the person drinking soy-milk is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1
4. the person watching spy movies is on the right of the person drinking soy-milk##1
5. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |      3      |      4       |
| Beverage           | 7up | soy-milk | coffee | iced-tea |
| Movie-Genre   | epic   | animation | spy         | martial-arts |

