.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-15::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: soul, country, dubstep, metal
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: adventure, documentary, family, mystery
1. the person watching adventure movies is on the right of the fan of country##1
2. the fan of metal is between the person watching mystery movies and the fan of soul##2
3. the fan of country is on the right of the fan of metal##1
4. the person watching documentary movies is on the left of the fan of metal##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3    |      4       |
| Music-Genre         | soul      | metal | country  | dubstep |
| Movie-Genre   | documentary | family  | mystery | adventure    |

