.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-16::.
There are 4 different nationalities: american, dutch, french, japanese
House: victorian, tower, townhouse, ranch-style
1. the ranch-style house is on the right of the tower house##1
2. the japanese is the townhouse house##1
3. the french is between the townhouse house and the dutch##2
4. the japanese is on the right of the french##1
5. the victorian house is on the left of the dutch##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2   |   3    |    4     |
| Nationality   | american | dutch | french | japanese |
| House     | victorian     | tower   | ranch-style | townhouse  |

