.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-18::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: collecting, puzzles, rock-climbing, singing
There are 4 different nationalities: spanish, colombian, japanese, egyptian
1. the colombian is on the right of the spanish##1
2. the spanish is on the far left##1
3. the person who's hobby is puzzles is between the spanish and the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##2
4. the person who's hobby is singing is the spanish##1
5. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the right of the egyptian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |    2    |       3       |     4      |
| Hobby       | singing | puzzles | rock-climbing | collecting |
| Nationality   | spanish    | colombian  | egyptian    | japanese       |

