.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-19::.
4 different pets are kept: pony, bird, turtle, lizard
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: baseball, basketball, golf, rowing
1. the person who's sport is basketball is on the left of the person who's sport is rowing##1
2. the person who's sport is baseball is on the left of the person who's sport is basketball##1
3. the owner of the lizard is the person who's sport is baseball##1
4. the person who's sport is rowing is between the owner of the pony and the owner of the turtle##2
5. the owner of the turtle is the person who's sport is golf##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |     3      |    4    |
| Pet   | lizard   | pony   | bird | turtle |
| Sport         | baseball | basketball | rowing     | golf    |

